</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_108_r1l20">Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> veſten / VVeygel Strobel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_108_r1l21"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> VVeygel als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / vvıe Jr dem Rate ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l22"><expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vor <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſoldn<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>Darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l23">kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> rate <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır alſo an den Rat bracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l24">dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> . eẅch ʒu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> . ſıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ır <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> . dıe Eſchenloer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l25">nehſt auf <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıef ʒu red geſacʒt / dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> . wıe Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l26"><expan>warnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . daʒ etlıch der ſtat veynd Jn <expan>ʒugreıffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l29"> als 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del> auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒeıt 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_108_line_1577028447339_585">ʒwen </ab></add> da <expan>fürrytte<ex>n</ex></expan> do <expan>weſte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe nıht / wer </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_109" id="53v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l1">die <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> alſbald Jn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> eẅr knecht ſagt / daʒ Jr das wert / Do <expan>lıeſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l2">ledıklıch <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>reıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>befulhe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm eẅch ʒu <expan>ſage<ex>n</ex></expan> . Jr bedörft kein far </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l3">vor Jn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd ſıe <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch nıht ʒu <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l4">denn guts / Das <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe eẅch nehſt alſo <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſo hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l5"><expan>nıema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> an ſıe <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / Denn wo wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l6">eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das teten wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l7">ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> <expan>A<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> etc xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l8"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd Peter dıe Haller </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l9">dıe <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vesten Weygel Strobel</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Weygel, als ir uns
                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir dem rate zu
                <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vor <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>soldn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ew kein
                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> rate <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sey etc., das
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir also an den rat bracht. Die
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ewch zu
                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, sie <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir
                <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, die Eschenloer, nehst auf
              <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief zu red gesaczt, die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            in <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, wie in <expan>warnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz etlich der stat veynd in
              <expan>zugreiffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, und als auf <expan>dies<ex>en</ex></expan> zeit
              <add>zwen</add> da <expan>fürrytte<ex>n</ex></expan>, do
              <expan>weste<ex>n</ex></expan> sie niht, wer <pb facs="#facs_109" id="53v"/>die
                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>. Alsbald in <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ewr knecht
            sagt, daz ir das wert, do <expan>liesse<ex>n</ex></expan> sie in lediklich
                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>reite<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>befulhe<ex>n</ex></expan> im, ewch zu
                <expan>sage<ex>n</ex></expan>, ir bedörft kein far vor in
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und sie <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht zu <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> denn guts. Das <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> sie ewch
            nehst also <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so hab <expan>niema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> kein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> an sie
                <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
              <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, das teten wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>
<expan>a<ex>nn</ex><hi rend="sup">o</hi></expan> etc. xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.<lb/><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und Peter die Haller die
                <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>.</ab>
</div>
